rows.label: qst202713_msg0001
rows.name: Mo mo mo! Why, why, mo!

rows.label: qst202713_msg0002
rows.name:
Germon only wanted to change
this dying world, mo!

rows.label: qst202713_msg0003
rows.name: So why did you...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202713_msg0004
rows.name:
That wasn't a demon,
just a regular monster.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0005
rows.name:
It was hungry, saw you all,
and just tried to eat you.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0006
rows.name:
It's not something that
would save the world.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0007
rows.name: Mo mo mo...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202713_msg0008
rows.name:
Hey...[ML:Dash ] Do you really
want to save the world?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0009
rows.name:
Yes, mo. That's why I gathered
the young Nopon who are
dissatisfied with Alst, mo.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0010
rows.name: You have the power to unite people.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0011
rows.name:
Next time, don't rely on
demons. Use that power to
change the world with everyone.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0012
rows.name: I think that's much cooler.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0013
rows.name: Mo mo mo...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202713_msg0014
rows.name:
More importantly, is a
Nopon named Mimumu here?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0015
rows.name:
Mimumu? There is no
such child here, mo.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0016
rows.name: Then where is Mimumu?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0017
rows.name: She might be in another branch, mo.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0018
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]What?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0019
rows.name: There are other groups doing this?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0020
rows.name:
Yes, mo. Germon is the representative
of the Superbia branch, mo.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0021
rows.name:
We were planning to summon three
demons together with the other
branches to change the world, mo.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0022
rows.name:
By the way, this one is the weakest
of the three demons, mo...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202713_msg0023
rows.name:
In the end, no demon was
summoned, though...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202713_msg0024
rows.name: Where are the other branches?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0025
rows.name:
One is the Gula branch. I heard
they perform their ritual deep
in the Wrecc Marshland, mo.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0026
rows.name:
The other one...[ML:Dash ] I wasn't told to
prevent information leaks, mo.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0027
rows.name:
I see. So the representative of
the Gula branch would know.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0028
rows.name: We should hurry to Gula.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0029
rows.name: Right...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202713_msg0030
rows.name:
Mimumu might be there, and if
they're summoning another hungry
monster, we have to save them.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0031
rows.name: Then, let's go.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0032
rows.name:
Please wait, mo. Germon was
impressed by your coolness, mo.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0033
rows.name:
If you'd like, please stay at
this branch and guide us, mo!

rows.label: qst202713_msg0034
rows.name: No thanks.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0035
rows.name: Why, mo?!

rows.label: qst202713_msg0036
rows.name:
I'm not the type to be a
leader, and I'm not
interested in changing Alst.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0037
rows.name: Mo mo mo, what should Germon do...?[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202713_msg0038
rows.name:
I told you, you have the
power to lead people. Just
use it for something good.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0039
rows.name: I'm sure Alst will change then.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0040
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]I understand, mo. Germon will
try to start from scratch, mo.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0041
rows.name:
Without relying on gods or demons,
with our own strength, mo!

rows.label: qst202713_msg0042
rows.name: That's the spirit. Good luck.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0043
rows.name:
Now, let's go deep into the
Wrecc Marshland in Gula.
